---
import PageLayout from '../../layouts/PageLayout.astro';
import Section from '../../components/astro/Section.astro';
---

<PageLayout
  title="Refund Policy | ZurichJS"
  description="ZurichJS Refund Policy for workshops, events, and merchandise."
  keywords={['ZurichJS', 'JavaScript Zurich', 'refund policy', 'ticket refund', 'workshop refund', 'merchandise']}
>
  <Section variant="white" padding="lg">
    <div class="animate-fade-in-up max-w-3xl mx-auto">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Refund Policy</h1>
      <p class="text-gray-500 mb-8">Our policies for refunds on workshops, events, and merchandise.</p>

      <div class="space-y-8">
        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Workshop &amp; Event Tickets</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-4">
            We understand that plans can change. Below is our policy for handling ticket refunds and transfers for paid ZurichJS workshops and events.
          </p>

          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">Ticket Transfers</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-4">
            If you are unable to attend an event, you may transfer your ticket to another person at no additional cost. To arrange a transfer, please email us at
            <a href="mailto:hello@zurichjs.com" class="text-yellow-600 hover:text-yellow-700 underline">hello@zurichjs.com</a>
            with the name and email address of the new attendee at least 48 hours before the event.
          </p>

          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">Refund Exceptions</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-3">
            While tickets are generally non-refundable, we offer full refunds in the following circumstances:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-4">
            <li><strong>Event cancellation:</strong> If ZurichJS cancels an event, all ticket holders will receive a full refund.</li>
            <li><strong>Significant date or venue change:</strong> If the event date or location changes substantially and you can no longer attend, you are entitled to a full refund.</li>
            <li><strong>Duplicate purchase:</strong> If you accidentally purchase multiple tickets, we will refund the duplicates.</li>
          </ul>

          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">Processing</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
            Approved refunds will be processed within 10 business days and returned to the original payment method. To request a refund, please email
            <a href="mailto:hello@zurichjs.com" class="text-yellow-600 hover:text-yellow-700 underline">hello@zurichjs.com</a>
            with your order confirmation number and the reason for your request.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">T-Shirt &amp; Merchandise</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-3">
            For t-shirts and other ZurichJS merchandise:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
            <li>Merchandise orders can be cancelled for a full refund before they are shipped.</li>
            <li>Once an item has been shipped, refunds are only available if the item arrives damaged or defective.</li>
            <li>Size exchanges may be accommodated subject to stock availability. Please contact us within 14 days of receiving your order.</li>
            <li>Custom or personalized items are non-refundable.</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mt-3">
            For all merchandise-related inquiries, please contact
            <a href="mailto:hello@zurichjs.com" class="text-yellow-600 hover:text-yellow-700 underline">hello@zurichjs.com</a>.
          </p>
        </section>
      </div>

      <hr class="my-8 border-gray-200" />

      <p class="text-sm text-gray-400 mb-6">Last updated: March 2026</p>

      <a href="/" class="inline-flex items-center text-yellow-600 hover:text-yellow-700 font-medium">
        &larr; Back to Home
      </a>
    </div>
  </Section>
</PageLayout>
